 on grant + cash stipend\, 5 fellows over 2 years)\, Panavision Fellowship 
 ($60\,000 camera package)\, Sony Pictures Entertainment ($10\,000)\, Unive
 rsity of Arizona TFTV ($10\,000)\nDuration: Annual fellowship program\n\nM
 ore: https://www.filmindependent.org/programs/applications/?utm_source=art
 ificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
