UID:adrianna-newell-fellowship-artsrec-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260723T103547Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260731
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260801
SUMMARY:Deadline: Adrianna Newell Fellowship at Arts&Rec 2026
DESCRIPTION:Inaugural Adrianna Newell Fellowship\, a live/work studio resid
 ency in Stamford\, NY (Western Catskills) for October 2026\, with possible
  extension into November. Named for board member Adrianna Newell\, it invi
 tes queer lens-based artists working in photography and moving image with 
 an active\, research-driven or conceptually rich practice\, especially wor
 k engaging queer perspectives on land\, rurality and regional space\, or q
 ueer identity\, memory\, intimacy\, community and embodiment. Open to arti
 sts from everywhere. Fellows receive a 1000 sq ft studio with attached apa
 rtment\, a $1\,500 combined materials stipend and per diem\, and introduct
 ions to the local creative community\; an open-studio presentation\, artis
 t talk or public exhibition at the end is required. Travel\, especially in
 ternational\, is not funded (residents are encouraged to seek travel suppo
 rt elsewhere). Apply by emailing a single PDF (one-page description of you
 r work and planned project\, 10 to 20 work samples with short descriptions
 \, and a current CV) to programs@artsrec.org. Deadline: 31 July 2026\; not
 ices by end of August.\n\nOrganisation: Arts&Rec Inc\nLocation: Stamford\,
  NY (Western Catskills)\, USA\nAward: Live/work residency: use of a 1000 s
 q ft studio and attached apartment\, plus a $1\,500 total materials stipen
 d and per diem. Travel (especially international) is not funded. No applic
 ation fee.\nDuration: October 2026 (four weeks to two months\, based on pr
 oject needs\; possible extension into November)\n\nMore: https://www.nyfa.
 org/opportunities/opportunity-info/?title=call-for-applications%3A-the-adr
 ianna-newell-fellowship-at-arts%26rec%2C-october-2026&id=013e03ad-6edf-47f
 b-8d14-291bdc930a31&utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=refer
 ral
URL:https://www.nyfa.org/opportunities/opportunity-info/?title=call-for-app
 lications%3A-the-adrianna-newell-fellowship-at-arts%26rec%2C-october-2026&
 id=013e03ad-6edf-47fb-8d14-291bdc930a31&utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantd
 esk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Stamford\, NY (Western Catskills)\, USA
END:VEVENT
